import { Component } from 'react' import { withRouter } from 'react-router-dom' import { Navbar, Nav, Container, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap' import { Props, Path } from '../interface/Interfaces' class Navigation extends Component { private pathname = this.props.location.pathname private appName: string = 'DOMAS' private path: Path = { index: '/', login: '/login', profil: '/profil', info: '/info' } render = (): JSX.Element => { return (
Domas Website
Data Info Action Another action Something Login
